            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>+ <rs key="#Copy">Exemplum</rs> ex autentico relevatum. + In nomine domini
                        Dei eterni. Anno ab incarnacione domini nostri Iesu Christi millesimo CXXXV,
                        indicione XII, quintodecimo die mensis februaiii. Quem ad meritum anime mee
                        pertinere potest, necesse est mihi semper illud agere unde in hoc et in
                        futuro seculo plenam apud Dominum possim consegui mercedem. Ideo ego
                            <persName
                            key="#Marquis/duke #Salian #Testamentum #Slave #Landed_possessions #parentOf #Churches #Beneficium #Castle #Curtes #Feudum #Mansi"
                            ref="#people/3571">Albertus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Marquis/duke">marchio</rs>, qui professus sum ex nacione mea lege
                        vivere <rs key="#Salian">Salicha</rs>, volo et statuo omnes <rs key="#Slave"
                            >servos atque ancillas</rs> meas post hobitum meum esse <rs
                            key="#Freedman">liberos et absolutos ab omni vinculo servitutis</rs> et
                        cives <rs key="#Roman">Romanos</rs>, omni suo peculio eis concesso. <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">Terram</rs> quam a me tenent volo ut ab <rs
                            key="#Churches">ecclesia</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/2427">Sancti
                            Petri</orgName> de <placeName key="#Churches #Beneficium"
                            ref="#places/4139">Villanova</placeName> pro <rs key="#Beneficium"
                            >beneficio</rs> teneant, et serviant de suis negociis in <orgName
                            key="#Dioecesis #Mother_churches" ref="#juridical_persons/503"><rs
                                key="#Dioecesis #Mother_churches">episcopatu</rs>
                            <placeName
                                key="#Dioecesis #Mother_churches #Monasteries #Cities #Bishops #Castle #Curtes #Feudum"
                                ref="#places/59">Veronensi</placeName></orgName>
                        <orgName key="#Dioecesis #Mother_churches" ref="#juridical_persons/2428">et
                                <placeName key="#Dioecesis #Mother_churches" ref="#places/69"
                                >Vicentino</placeName></orgName>. Volo etiam <persName
                            ref="#people/3594" key="#childOf #Curtes">Bonefacium</persName> et
                            <persName ref="#people/3595" key="#childOf #Curtes"
                            >Garsendonium</persName>
                        <rs key="#childOf">filios</rs> meos habere quicquid mihi pertinet in
                            <geogName key="#Curtes #Mansi" ref="#estates/2089"><rs key="#Curtes"
                                >curte</rs> de <placeName key="#Curtes #Mansi" ref="#places/4140"
                                >Menervii</placeName></geogName>, exceptis duobus <rs key="#Mansi"
                            >mansis</rs> quos <persName ref="#people/3596"
                            key="#childOf #Mansi #Countess">Garsinde</persName> filie mee relinquo,
                        et <geogName ref="#estates/2092" key="#Curtes">de <placeName
                                ref="#places/4144" key="#Curtes #Churches"
                            >Zerpa</placeName></geogName>, necnon <geogName ref="#estates/2093"
                            key="#Curtes">de <placeName key="#Curtes" ref="#places/4149"
                                >Montecleda</placeName></geogName>, et in <placeName>Sancto Iohanne
                            Bretone</placeName>, illud Sancti Iohannis eorum parte pro feudo
                        possidente. <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/2001"
                            key="#Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Priests">Sanctus autem
                            Benedictus</orgName> habeat quicquid mihi pertinet <rs
                            key="#Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure">proprietario iure</rs> in <placeName
                            ref="#places/4141">Tresenta</placeName>, in <placeName
                            ref="#places/2990">Mulo</placeName> et in omnibus locis a <placeName
                            key="Rivers"><rs key="Rivers">flumine</rs> Athesis</placeName> usque ad
                        Ilbitum et Vadum de Capris. <rs key="#Monasteries">Monasterium</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/90">Sancti
                            Çenonis</orgName> et <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/2429"
                            key="#Monasteries">Sancte Trinitatis</orgName> et <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2430" key="#Monasteries">Sancti Firmi</orgName>
                        habeant quicquid mihi pertinet in <rs key="#Cities">civitate</rs> Verone vel
                        extra Veronam, usque ad Flubium, excepta terra quam habeo iuxta murum
                        civitatis quam <persName key="#Witness #Testamentum"><name
                                ref="Heinricus/de Artvico">Enrico</name></persName> de Artvicho ad
                        proprium relinquo, preterea <rs key="#Castle">castrum</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Castle #Curtes" ref="#places/4138">Sancti
                            Bonefacii</placeName> cum tota <geogName ref="#estates/2090"
                            key="#Curtes">curte</geogName>, exceptis tribus mansis quos Garsinde
                        iudico. Necnon castrum de <placeName key="#Castle #Curtes"
                            ref="#places/2477">Monteforte</placeName> cum tota <geogName
                            ref="#estates/2091" key="#Curtes">curte</geogName> episcopatui Verone
                        relinquo, eo silicet ordine ut <rs key="#Count">comes</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/3597" key="#Count #Castle #Curtes #Feudum"
                            >Albertus</persName> et <persName ref="#people/3598"
                            key="#Count #Castle #Curtes #Feudum #siblingOf">Rambaldus</persName> et
                            <persName ref="#people/3599" key="#Count #Castle #Curtes #Feudum"
                            >Bonefacius</persName> de <placeName ref="#places/4151"
                            >Magreda</placeName> habeant pro <rs key="#Feudum">feudo</rs> ex parte
                        eiusdem episcopatus, et serviant infra <placeName>Mincium</placeName> et
                            <placeName>Plavum</placeName>. Et si Rambaldus decesserit, <rs
                            key="#siblingOf">fratres</rs> eius cum eis comuniter habeant, et si
                        aliquis eorum sine filiis decesserit, unus alteri succedat. Similiter volo
                        ut isti tres habeant <placeName ref="#places/4150">Concam de Albaro</placeName> ad proprium et
                        persolvant <rs>dotem</rs>
                        <rs key="#Countess">comitisse</rs> Garsinde que ei iure debetur.
                                <persName><name ref="Marsilium">Marsilium</name></persName> vero et
                        filios <persName><name ref="Agnes">Agnetis</name></persName> volo ut habeant
                        totum quod mihi perlinet in <orgName key="#Dioecesis #Mother_churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/223">episcopatu <placeName
                                key="#Dioecesis #Mother_churches #Cities" ref="#places/41"
                                >Pataviensi</placeName></orgName> extra civitatem, ita ut Marsilius
                        medietatem habeat. Quicquid autem proprietatis mee in civitate est, <rs
                            key="#Hospitals">hospitale</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/2431" key="#Hospitals">Sancti
                            Sepulchri</orgName> de <placeName key="#Hospitals" ref="#places/914"
                            >Venecia</placeName> habeat. <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/2433"
                            key="#Churches">Ecclesia de <placeName ref="#places/259" key="#Churches"
                                >Runco</placeName></orgName> et <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1404" key="#Churches">de Zerpa</orgName> habeant
                        proprietatem <rs key="#Islands">insule</rs> de <placeName ref="#places/4142"
                            key="#Islands">Scardevara</placeName>, usufructum autem Bonefacio
                        propinquo meo si decessero usque dum vivit relinquo; similiter volo ut omnes
                        res quas mihi donavit in eum deveniant. Insuper statuo terram quam habeo in
                            <placeName ref="#places/4143">Montebello</placeName> et per totum
                        Vicentinum episcopatum a Montebello in territorio <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2432">Sancti Felicis</orgName> episcopatus
                        habeat. Terra de Conca de Albaro quam filii Bosketti a me tenent ecclesia
                            <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/504" key="#Churches">Sancte
                            Zacharie</orgName> habeat, ita ut ipsi pro feudo teneant ***. Signa
                        manuum <persName ref="#people/3700" key="#Bishops #Witness #Testamentum"><rs
                                key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs> Veronensis</persName>, <rs
                            key="#Abbots">abas</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/2434" key="#Abbots">Calavene</orgName>, <rs key="#Archpriests"
                            >archipresbiter</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Archpriests">Sancti Georgii</orgName>, <rs key="#Priests"
                            >presbiter</rs>
                        <persName key="#Priests #Witness #Testamentum"><name
                                ref="Richardus/de Sancto Benedicto">Richardus</name></persName> de
                        Sancto Benedicto <rs key="#Witness">testes</rs>. Signa manuum <persName
                            key="#Witness #Testamentum"><name ref="Ardericu/de Montesello"
                                >Ardericus</name></persName> de Montesello, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Testamentum"><name ref="Heinricus/de Bonadico"
                                >Enricus</name></persName> de <placeName ref="#places/4154">Bonadico</placeName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Testamentum"><name ref="Guiscardus/de Noventa"
                                >Wiçardus</name></persName> de <placeName ref="#places/4153">Noventa</placeName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Testamentum"><name ref="Ambrosius"
                            >Ambrosius</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness #Testamentum"
                                ><name ref="Nordellus/de Lunico">Nordillus</name></persName> de
                        <placeName ref="#places/4155">Lunico</placeName> testes. Signa manuum <persName key="#Witness #Testamentum"><name
                                ref="Benenatus">Benenatus</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Testamentum"><name ref="Hugo/de Zerpa"
                            >Ugo</name></persName> de Çerpa,Enricus de Artvicho
                        <rs>iurisperiti</rs>, <persName key="#Witness #Testamentum"><name
                                ref="Caverlattus">Caverlattus</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Testamentum"><name ref="Hubertus/de Zerpa"
                            >Ubertus</name></persName> de Çerpa, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Testamentum"><name ref="Paganus/de Sancto Bonefacio"
                                >Paganus</name></persName> de Sancto Bonefacio testes. Ego <persName
                            key="#Notary #Testamentum #Writer"><name ref="Albertus"
                            >Albertus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> hanc <rs key="#Testamentum"
                            >ordinacionem</rs> rogatus <rs key="#Writer">scripsi</rs> et complevi. </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
